{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Overview</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Misa</i> is a sorceress finding her way in a colorful  fantasy world sprinkled with french expressions. To fight your way through, you will build spells by combining multiples effects and items to increase their power. Make a good use of all your resources to end up victorious ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/Fight.gif?t=1737574718\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><br>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Travel through 3 biomes</strong> each with its boss and monsters that have unique abilities.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/Biome.gif?t=1737574718\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Create your own spells</strong> and build using looted items :<br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 50+ effects to stack buffs and debuffs onto your targets<br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 30+ cores to determine your spells actions &amp; spells bonuses<br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 30+ relics that grants you a passive bonus for the whole run</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/Spell.gif?t=1737574718\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Each destination is a resource</strong> in itself, so optimize your path to use them wisely. Will you risk starting by the dungeon to get new cores or use one of the few shops to upgrade your spells first ?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/Destination.gif?t=1737574718\" /></p><p c